{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733710/extras/GifDrTop.gif?t=1726570127\" /><br><strong>DEATHRAY</strong> - It's a complete immersion into the terrifying atmosphere of the exclusion zone. The photorealistic effect intensifies the sense of danger. You find yourself in a secret bio laboratory that has been the subject of terrifying rumors. Everyone who attempted to investigate it was declared missing without a trace.<br><br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733710/extras/DRgif124e.gif?t=1726570127\" /><br><br><strong>STORYLINE</strong><br>You're forcibly sent on Investigation No. 305. Upon regaining consciousness, you discover clues for solving puzzles and exploring further. Due to toxins in the lab and cognitive brain damage, the character experiences hallucinations, hears voices, and sounds. To enlighten the mind, the character finds a camera whose pictures depict reality without hallucinations. However, it turns out that the mutants hunting them are real. Therefore, be cautious and listen carefully to the sounds.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733710/extras/NewDRGif7.gif?t=1726570127\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733710/extras/NewDRGIF2.gif?t=1726570127\" /><br><br><strong>QUESTS</strong><br>Look for clues, think logically, pay attention to details. This will help you solve the quests on the map as quickly as possible, and get important items<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733710/extras/DrGif11.gif?t=1726570127\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2733710/extras/NewDRGIF1.gif?t=1726570127\" /><br><br><strong>CHARACTERS:</strong><br>Over